{"title": "Generate TGT", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "smb-protocol/generate-tgt", "html": "<h1 id=\"generate-tgt\">Generate TGT</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>netexec smb <target> -u <username> -p <password> --generate-tgt /path</p>\n<p>export KRB5CCNAME=/path</p>\n<p>netexec smb <target> -u <username> -k --use-kcache</p>\n</blockquote>", "excerpt": "Generate TGT netexec smb -u -p --generate-tgt /path export KRB5CCNAME=/path netexec smb -u -k --use-kcache", "tags": []}